{"tid":2129602,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[大屠殺]深水埗鬥魚店　遭3大漢淋紅油刑毀","createTime":"2020-07-28T16:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T02:34:13.000Z","uid":69518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1321773a4bafa234ace70cac59a7bbaffbb2b153","tid":2129602,"uid":69518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T16:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n深水埗汝州街63號地下一間售賣泰國鬥魚店舖，今日(28日)下午4時許，3名男子闖入店內，向職員大叫「不要動」後，即二話不說向多個養有鬥魚的魚缸潑紅色漆油，他們得手後迅速逃離現場，姓吳(33歲)男負責人見狀報警。<br />\n警方到場調查，翻查看店舖內閉路電視錄影，從片段可見，3名男子進店後，其中2人手拿盛有漆油的紙杯，向多個魚缸淋潑紅油，並將紙杯掟在店內，然後迅速逃去，過程約10多秒。警方將案件列刑毀，交深水埗警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200728/mobile/bkn-20200728191629337-0728_00822_001.html#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200728%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200728191629337-0728_00822_001.html%23%26gid%3D1%26pid%3D4&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=b3d13e31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200728/mobile/bkn-20200728191629337-0728_00822_001.html#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vBZkjV1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvBZkjV1.png&h=cc0c3c62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6668bb3834d473e43d3077e9b05b65b641b98251","tid":2129602,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T17:01:08.000Z","msg":"想問其實咩事？<br />\n政治？普通仇口？"},{"pid":"1dca41d58ebcbe1355c39164eeb71b562dd49d6b","tid":2129602,"uid":126317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T17:14:36.000Z","msg":"唉，唔覺意㩒左東網條link添⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986b6b668e0b7276071f737cc689f8c2cb94e76b","tid":